### Register user test2
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test Deux",
  "avatarColor": "#FFA502"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("test2AccessToken", response.body.accessToken);
  client.global.set("test2RefreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
  client.global.set("test2Id", response.body.user.id);
%}

### Login as test2 (if already registered)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test2@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("test2AccessToken", response.body.accessToken);
  client.global.set("test2RefreshToken", response.body.refreshToken);
  client.global.set("test2Id", response.body.user.id);
%}

### Send friend request from test2 to the target user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/friendships
Authorization: Bearer {{test2AccessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "addresseeId": "3b5069ef-4033-4bb1-a625-bf29ee8dc17b"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("test2FriendshipId", response.body.id);
%}

### Check pending requests sent (as target user, run auth.http login first)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/friendships/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}